com.yworks.yfiles.layout.hierarchic

Class IncrementalHintItemMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.ItemMapping<TItem,TValue>
      • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.ContextItemMapping<IModelItem,Object,IIncrementalHintsFactory>
        • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.hierarchic.IncrementalHintItemMapping

  • public final class IncrementalHintItemMapping
extends ContextItemMapping<IModelItem,Object,IIncrementalHintsFactory>
    Provides different ways to define a mapping from model items to incremental hints for use with HierarchicLayoutData.

    Only one of the provided ways to define a mapping can be used at the same time, therefore only one of the properties of this class should be set on an instance.
